<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Aug1932"><font color="red">28 August 1932</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Will you please send me by return the <i>carnet</i> I left in your house &hellip; I am trying to paint up section I of Prt II for October <i>transition</i> in order to repay the Jolases for their kindness &hellip; I got Gilbert to open one of my boxes in Passy and send me 15 other <i>carnets</i>. </div>
